The new version of DiDi Food will bring a new store page to provide you with a better service:
1. New store page visual upgrade
2. Support searching for dishes in the store, making selection more convenient
3. The picture of the dish supports enlargement, and the food is clearer
4. Single-standard dishes can be purchased directly, ordering is smoother
5. Sub-options for dish specifications support multiple selections
...
The new version does not stop there, more functions are waiting for you to experience!
